      • Pinboard

        public Pinboard​(int levelNum,
                java.lang.String levelType,
                java.lang.String leftNum,
                java.util.ArrayList<javafx.scene.layout.HBox> text)
        Creates a new Pinboard
        Parameters:
        levelNum - could be 1-6 inclusive
        levelType - could be "profile" or "chatbox". Each type is made completely differently and this difference is dealt with inside of this constructor
        leftNum - number of questions left in a chatbox level
        text - the text that had already been written in chatbox
